Full-length, Peaceville Records
February 1992	

Fenriz - drums
Nocturno Culto - vocals, guitar
Zephyrous - guitar
Dag Nilsen - session bass

Recorded in 1991 but released in the beginning of 1992.

first press 1992 (VILE 28 CD): white disc (lim. to 2000)
second press 1992 (VILE 28 CD): black disc
Third press with Music for Nations with number CDVILE 28. Then with Snapper
Music.

The beginning of Darkthrone&#039;s black metal material.

Reissued and remastered in 2003 as a digipak featuring a video interview clip.

This remastered CD version 2003 also released in 2007 by Black Metal Attack
Records from Brazil for South America.
